<section id='aviso-section'>
  <header>
    <span class='icono'>
      <svg
        width='24'
        height='24'
        viewBox='0 0 28 28'
        fill='none'
        xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
        <circle cx='14' cy='14' r='13' fill='#fffbe6' stroke='#e6c800' stroke-width='2'></circle>
        <path d='M14 8v7' stroke='#e6c800' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round'></path>
        <circle cx='14' cy='19' r='1.5' fill='#e6c800'></circle>
      </svg>
    </span>
    <h3>ATENCIÓN</h3>
    <button aria-label='Cerrar aviso' class='close'>&times;</button>
  </header>
  <p>
    Los acordes han sido migrados automáticamente desde el blog antiguo. Puede haber errores de
    formato o acordes. Si detectas alguno, <a href='/contacto'> avísanos</a>.
  </p>

  <style>
    section {
      position: absolute;
      top: 16px;
      right: 12px;
      z-index: 20;
      max-width: 340px;
      background: #fffbe6;
      color: #7a5c00;
      border: 1px solid #ffe58f;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      padding: 12px 40px 12px 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;

      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #e6c800;
      margin: 0 0 2px 0;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      & .icono {
      }
    }

    p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #7a5c00;
      line-height: 1.1;

      & a {
        color: var(--link-color);
        font-weight: bold;
        text-decoration: none;

        &:hover {
          color: var(--link-hover-color);
        }
      }
    }
    .close {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      color: #7a5c00;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      position: absolute;
      top: 8px;
      right: 10px;
      line-height: 1;
      padding: 0;
    }
  </style>
</section>
<script>
  window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
    var closeBtn = document.querySelector('.close');
    var aviso = document.querySelector('#aviso-section');
    if (closeBtn && aviso) {
      closeBtn.addEventListener('click', function () {
        aviso.style.display = 'none';
      });
    }
  });
</script>
